HOST: http://lifebelt.apiblueprint.org/

# lifebelt

Lifebelt is teachers's lifebelt to simplify
publish, share and review homework and exam assignments. Also helps students,
giving them easy way to follow and be inform about new tasks, receiving
instant review whenever is possible.

